description: TEHRAN – Iranian shot putter Rashid Masjedi passed away due to tongue cancer at the age of 35 on Thursday.
title: Iranian Para athlete Masjedi dies at age of 35

description: TEHRAN - Al Riyadi successfully defended its FIBA WASL-West Asia League championship after beating Shahrdari Gorgan, 100-78, in the winner-take-all Game 3 of the Final, Wednesday night at a packed Stade Nouhad Nowfal in Zouk Mikael.
title: Shahrdari runners-up at FIBA WASL-West Asia
